s97hpqFaUs-3UnvYA">Cao Khải</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Thanh-T%C3%A2m-t%C3%A0i-nh%C3%A2n/Th%E1%BA%ADp-b%E1%BA%A5t-h%C3%A0i-k%E1%BB%B3-09/poem-wN45DJ0ZB5nlxoJKmQBbvA">Thập bất hài kỳ 09 - 十不諧其九</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Thanh-T%C3%A2m-t%C3%A0i-nh%C3%A2n/author-Ry0GXj_uifS6AejvZUIukQ">Thanh Tâm tài nhân</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-Di-T%C3%B4n/Thi%C3%AAn-Du-qu%C3%A1n-V%E1%BA%A1n-Phong-%C4%91%C3%ACnh/poem-QW3SIuM9zjSd3AwL0YuRog">Thiên Du quán Vạn Phong đình - 天遊觀萬峰亭</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-Di-T%C3%B4n/author-edTceA8S1YU0BsK54Tjq9Q">Chu Di Tôn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Tu%E1%BB%B3-Ch%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-l%C6%B0u-h%E1%BA%ADu-T%C3%A2n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-h%E1%BB%99i-t%E1%BB%91ng-ch%C6%B0-qu%C3%A2n/poem-BHWjbd5zPl5dHd8pHlzozA">Tuỳ Chương lưu hậu Tân Đình hội tống chư quân - 隨章留後新亭會送諸君</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
